OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FThe Government has announced a #50
OL,8,Fmillion investment to help protect
OL,9,FSomerset's homes, farms and businesses
OL,10,Ffrom flooding.
OL,12,FSomerset Council is being given the
OL,13,Fmoney to strengthen the county's flood
OL,14,Fdefences and improve its drainage,
OL,15,Fafter it was forced to declare a major
OL,16,Fincident in January, because of the
OL,17,Fimpact of severe weather.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
