FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FFloods Minister Emma Hardy will
OL,8,Fofficially deliver the news at the
OL,9,FFlood and Coast Conference today. She
OL,10,Fvisited Somerset in February, and has
OL,11,Facknowledged that the county has
OL,12,F"faced the full force of extreme
OL,13,Fweather this year."
OL,15,FThe Government says the funding will
OL,16,Freduce the burden on emergency
OL,17,Fresponders and help communities
OL,18,Fwithstand future incidents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FThe investment will be provided
OL,8,Fdirectly to Somerset Council to fund a
OL,9,Frange of flood resilience measures,
OL,10,Fsuch as improved drainage
OL,11,Finfrastructure, enhanced flood defence
OL,12,Fschemes and better watercourse
OL,13,Fmaintenance.
OL,15,FEarlier this year the county
OL,16,Fexperienced its second wettest January
OL,17,Fon record, with more than double the
OL,18,Faverage rainfall. Previous years have
OL,19,Fseen communities devastated by rising
OL,20,Fwaters and major clearup operations
OL,21,Fonce they return to normal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FEmma Hardy said: "The communities here
OL,8,Fdeserve more than a temporary fix
OL,9,Fwhich is why this government is
OL,10,Finvesting.
OL,12,F"This #50 million funding in the
OL,13,Fprotection of homes, farms and
OL,14,Flivelihoods in Somerset for years to
OL,15,Fcome."
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@AOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
