OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FA Government statement refers to
OL,8,FSomerset as "one of England's most
OL,9,Fimportant agricultural counties"
OL,10,Fadding that "Repeated flooding
OL,11,Fthreatens the viability of farming
OL,12,Fcommunities across the region."
OL,14,FSomerset Council Leader Bill Revans
OL,15,Fhas welcomed the investment, saying
OL,16,Fthe council is "pleased the Government
OL,17,Fhas listened to our calls for urgent
OL,18,Faction and welcome this vital
OL,19,Finvestment into the future of
OL,20,FSomerset".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
