OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,F"This winter has shown how Somerset's
OL,8,Funique environment is particularly
OL,9,Fsusceptible to the impacts of climate
OL,10,Fchange and it is clear we must help
OL,11,Four communities to adapt and become
OL,12,Fmore resilient," he said.
OL,14,F"We will work closely with partners,
OL,15,Fincluding the Environment Agency,
OL,16,FSomerset Rivers Authority, Internal
OL,17,FDrainage Board, Natural England and,
OL,18,Fmost importantly, our local
OL,19,Fcommunities, to ensure these funds are
OL,20,Finvested wisely to provide lasting
OL,21,Fbenefits for years to come."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FSomerset Council says some of the
OL,8,Femerging themes will include reviewing
OL,9,Fand learning from recent flood events
OL,10,Facross Somerset, engineering and
OL,11,Finfrastructure improvements in high-
OL,12,Frisk areas, natural flood management
OL,13,Fschemes, support for property-level
OL,14,Fflood protection, and improved
OL,15,Fcollaboration with local communities.
OL,17,FThe next step will be to develop
OL,18,Fproposals and engagement before any
OL,19,Fschemes are taken forward for delivery.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
