OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781097082
OL,3,C#50m Government investment to protect
OL,4,CSomerset from threat of serious
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FCllr Revans added: "This is a
OL,8,Ffantastic opportunity and we know our
OL,9,Fcommunities will want to input into
OL,10,Fthe programme to ensure we are taking
OL,11,Ffull advantage of the funding. We're
OL,12,Fat a very early stage and we look
OL,13,Fforward to engaging with our residents
OL,14,Fand businesses as we develop a clear
OL,15,Fplan for delivery."
OL,26,@oD@TOUwD@SO]
